      "raceComments": "{\"comment\":\"8. BOOM BAM SHIFTY wasn't far away at the finish when 5th and beaten only 5 lengths (26.45) at Temora. Tough to beat if on-song. 5. ZIPPING PERCAT was an effortless winner in quick time two back then got home into the frame when second at The Gardens (30.32) last time. Hard to beat again. 7. SNEAKY MOUSE is a talented type and proved too strong last time to win by 1.75 lengths at this track in a handy 25.16 beating Jungle Miss. Ran one of the fastest times on the program in her latest win. Looks a key chance if runs up to latest figure. 1. WONGABOORI BELLE was out of the money at this circuit last start but can make amends.\",\"runners\":[8,5,7,1],\"exclusive\":false}",
